	Simplify.
	(proced-omit-processes): Use use-region-p.
	(proced-sort-pcpu, proced-sort-pmem, proced-sort-pid)
	(proced-sort-start, proced-sort-time, proced-sort-user):
	Use proced-sort-interactive.
