	* emacs-lisp/byte-opt.el (byte-compile-trueconstp)
	(byte-compile-nilconstp): Can't use recursion in a defsubst.

	* textmodes/tex-mode.el (latex-mode): Remove % from paragraph-separate
	so that M-q can fill comments.
